'''Ebonite''' was a black substance used to make the tops of desks. [[Supreme Chancellor/Legends|Supreme Chancellor]] [[Palpatine/Legends|Palpatine]]'s desk and the floor in the private office in his [[Chancellor's Suite/Legends|private suite]] were made of ebonite.

